MissionFlowTrigger.description: When PreBossWave1 has been Completed, Activate EliminateBoss1
When EliminateBoss1 has been Completed, Activate PreBossWave2
When PreBossWave2 has been Completed, Activate EliminateBoss2
When EliminateBoss2 has been Completed, Activate PreBossWave3
When PreBossWave3 has been Completed, Activate EliminateBoss3
When EliminateBoss3 has been Completed, Activate PreBossWave4
When PreBossWave4 has been Completed, Activate EliminateBoss4
When EliminateBoss4 has been Completed, Complete Mission
